title: IAA Tonight | Kevin Durant and the Nets Agree to 'Move Forward'
description: Kevin Durant and the Brooklyn Nets ownership have agreed to end his trade request and move forward with the upcoming season, but how long will this relationship actually last? Countdown to Kickoff continues with the New England Patriots. Will Mac Jones make a leap in year two, or is he bound to hit a sophomore slump?
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Ashley Nicole Moss, Brandon Flowers, Omar Kelly)
